{
  "stem": "7744.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, and I guess they needed, maybe, her other skills that she had, which were skills in writing and, and speaking and whatever.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After Plaszow, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] after Plaszow, it was already-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we went with the transports when they were sending the transports.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother and I went to, to Skarzysko-Kamienna where they had an ammunition factory, and from there to Tschenstochau, Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And those were camps, labor camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They made ammunitions in those.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Skarzysko-Kamienna, they, they made bullets, I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In, in fact, some people would get sort of a yellow color to them from the powders that were used, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in those camps, in one of those camps, I was cleaning a Gestapo's shoes, or I don't know if he was a Gestapo or if he wasn't, but he was a soldier, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I-- sometimes, from time to time, I remember him giving me a very beautifully thin kind of sandwich that they had, these little sandwiches that were very elegant, which I wasn't familiar with [LAUGHS] at the time.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In fact, I don't ever-- I'm never familiar with thin sandwiches, since I always have thick sandwiches.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But in those days in the other camps, I was very much protected by my mother, so as to make sure that, that I lived.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because there was no place to hide.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was hunger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was fear.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there were selections.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And people died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, and one never knew from day to day what the day would hold.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it depended on what kind of commandant came into the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So it was very hard, very hard.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
